title: Andy Murray no match for ruthless Novak Djokovic - Sthelensstar.co.uk
text:
Novak Djokovic produced an inspired display to thrash a chastened Andy Murray 6-1 6-3 and reach the final of the Shanghai Masters. The world number one broke his Scottish opponent three times in the first set and then hit back from a break down in the second to wrap up victory inside 68 minutes.
 Sthelensstar.co.uk.
